org.firstinspires.ftc.robotcore.internal.network

Class WifiDirectDeviceNameManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.firstinspires.ftc.robotcore.internal.network.WifiStartStoppable
      • org.firstinspires.ftc.robotcore.internal.network.WifiDirectDeviceNameManager
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DeviceNameManager

    public class WifiDirectDeviceNameManager
extends WifiStartStoppable
implements DeviceNameManager
    WifiDirectDeviceNameManager manages the name by which the current device (robot controller or driver station) is known externally. By default, it tracks the WifiDirect name of the device.
